    "en": {
      "name": "Live\u2606Twin Lil-la Sweet",
      "effect": "When your opponent activates a card or effect in response to the activation of your \"Live\u2606Twin\" card or effect (Quick Effect): You can discard this card; negate that opponent's effect. If this card is in your GY and you control a \"Ki-sikil\" monster: You can Special Summon this card, but while it is face-up in the Monster Zone, you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck, except Fiend monsters. You can only use each effect of \"Live\u2606Twin Lil-la Sweet\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
